		<p>RBS has a branch in the USA? Weird&#8230; never thought that would extend out of, y&#8217;know, SCOTLAND. </p>
<p>Is there money in the ATM on the closed lane? Just wondering if they decided that maybe the cost of running the ATM wasn&#8217;t worth having it, and shut it down as a test. If there&#8217;s money still in the thing, though, really begins to make you wonder&#8230;</p>
<p>I&#8217;m also wondering what a &#8220;cash option&#8221; is. You received a cheque &#8212; something used to represent cash &#8212; to take to a bank, and they can&#8217;t turn it into cash? There are some really bizarre arcane rules in banks that just make me wonder sometimes.</p>

		
