<p>My sympathies, man. Yours definitely outdoes mine. That&#8217;s a rather crappy situation, and unless you have someone on the other end who can help you out, I&#8217;m not sure what else you could do. I take it BMO&#8217;s &lt;sarcasm&gt;ever so helpful&lt;/sarcasm&gt; Direct Banking is of no help, eh?</p>

		
