	<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-24000">
		<div id="comment-24000">
		<div class="comment-gravatar"><img alt='' src='//1.gravatar.com/avatar/7e3ebd32cd6ec15d231d15124d17f84a?s=65&#038;d=mm&#038;r=x' srcset='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/7e3ebd32cd6ec15d231d15124d17f84a?s=130&amp;d=mm&amp;r=x 2x' class='avatar avatar-65 photo' height='65' width='65' /></div>

		<div class="comment-body">
		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<cite class="fn">Mughal</cite><br/>
		<a href="http://www.sowrey.org/2007/11/bank-of-montreal-i-hate-your-security/#comment-24000">
			26 August 2013 at 08:29</a>		</div><!-- .comment-meta .commentmetadata -->

		<p>It seems the &#8216;Techies&#8217; have no knowledge of the real world, nor any people skills, nor any concept of customer service.  The Techies themselves have transformed themselves into un-thinking automatons ((IMO). And yet the executives draw outrageous salaries and the bank charges exorbitant fees and what do the depositors get, lousy service!</p>

		
